'''Marco Battagli''' or '''Marcus de Battaglis''' (died 1370/76) was a historian from [[Rimini]] in North Eastern Italy.<ref>{{emc1|Marie Bláhová|Battagli, Marco, of Rimini|147-148}}</ref> He wrote a universal chronicle in Latin.

